    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What is the DAC Platform?" class="article-title">
          What is the DAC Platform?
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:24:16Z" title="2025-12-08T18:24:16Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:24</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47027536110739-What-is-the-DAC-Platform/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>The <strong>DAC Platform</strong> is Star Atlas’s official on-chain system for managing player-created organizations known as <strong>Decentralized Autonomous Corporations (DACs)</strong>. It serves as the foundation for collaborative play, enabling individuals to formally unite under shared goals and values.</p><p>While gameplay integration is still in development, the platform already supports the creation, branding, and discovery of DACs, helping players organize today, and prepare for deeper social and strategic systems coming in the future.</p><p><img class="wysiwyg-image-resized hs-image-align-none" style="aspect-ratio: 688/361; height: auto; width: 688px;" src="https://20489070.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/20489070/image-png-May-01-2025-04-10-12-7005-PM.png" width="688" height="361"></p><h3 id="h_01KBG3V7J155TD1XC58PWZBMAS">What Does the DAC Platform Do?</h3><p>The DAC Platform at <a href="https://play.staratlas.com/dac" target="_new" rel="noopener">play.staratlas.com/dac</a> allows players to:</p><ul>
<li><p><strong>Register a DAC</strong> with a unique name and visual identity</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Write a public description</strong> and outline their mission or values</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Create custom tags</strong> for filtering and discoverability</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Generate a join link</strong> to recruit new members</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Explore other DACs</strong> based on faction, focus, or philosophy</p></li>
</ul><p>Each DAC is stored <strong>on-chain</strong>, meaning its data is secure, permanent, and transparently managed within the Star Atlas ecosystem.</p><h3 id="h_01KBG3V7J19TBQ1PAN5KYST9NZ">Key Features</h3><ul>
<li><p><strong>Name, Avatar &amp; Cover</strong><br>Represent your DAC with a visual identity and a name that reflects your vision in Galia.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Public Description</strong><br>Share your story, gameplay focus, and expectations with potential recruits.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Custom Tags</strong><br>Add tags like “Mining,” “Freight,” “Combat,” or “Ustur” to help players find organizations that match their interests and values.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Join URL</strong><br>Instantly recruit members with a personalized DAC invite link.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Public Discovery</strong><br>Browse the full DAC registry, review their tags, and apply to join the one that fits you best.</p></li>
</ul><blockquote><p>⚠️ <strong>Note:</strong> The current version of the DAC Platform is not yet tied to in-game utility. However, it lays the groundwork for major gameplay systems to come.</p></blockquote><h3 id="h_01KBG3V7J1Z7V50DXAWM7R7C0J">What’s Coming Next?</h3><p>Future DAC Platform updates will unlock powerful features like:</p><ul>
<li><p>Treasury and financial tools</p></li>
<li><p>Member roles and advanced permissions</p></li>
<li><p>Shared asset and resource management</p></li>
<li><p>On-chain proposal voting systems</p></li>
<li><p>In-game integrations with SAGE and UE5</p></li>
</ul><p>These updates will position DACs as <strong>fully functioning guilds</strong> with the tools to strategize, build, govern, and thrive together in the Star Atlas metaverse.</p></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

